      <title>Have you ever seen a cats eye reflect in 800mm macro lens? The glow of light ins...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DRE22IciCXH/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/582461055_18106967680609681_5507458579997012247_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc2NjM3NjM4NDI2NDk2MTM5NA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Q59rx3D-q4wQ7kNvwHJyyQM&amp;_nc_oc=Ado9vGeSGDS_71ouIk-VzdBT0aZoYQkoY0Uk3rZ3GoY8KmKZ8wTwkXcL33BMRcBUX_4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=UwM3YyDEwXsxytinv9HU4g&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzeVSP6RIjE6qOPfp8JZOVYNEtneK0wNLmgqOdFrq4RYQ&amp;oe=69C9C23E" alt="Instagram billede fra @theunseenalchemist" /></p><p><strong>@theunseenalchemist</strong></p><p>Have you ever seen a cats eye reflect in 800mm macro lens? <br/>
<br/>
The glow of light inside a cats eye is caused by light bouncing off the tapetum lucidum, a layer of crystal - containing cells located behind the retina. <br/>
<br/>
2 years ago I was honoured to sit patiently alongside @timflachphotography and my gorgeous Devon Rex cat @gobbolinothewitchescat to try to capture a reflective cats eye under macro lens for the first time. <br/>
<br/>
Using some tips from shooting reflective materials I’d picked up along the way with @theunseenbeauty and Tim’s incredible experience after 3 days the shot was caught! <br/>
<br/>
A 100mm lens wasn’t viable, as the reflection required atleast 3m of distance, instead Tim flew in a rare canon 800mm RF lens, with additional close up rings and a high speed broncolor ring flash to ignite the reflection. <br/>
<br/>
Included as part of the wonderful new book Feline out now! <br/>
<br/>
Well done Gobbi for staying still (eventually) <br/>
<br/>
#cat #catseye #timflach #catphoto #catlover #macro #caturday #photographer #nature #naturephotography #animalphotography</p>]]></description>
